<div class="left-panel-step-5"></div>


<div class="container-fluid custom-container top-margin-adjustment-for-fixed-navbar">
    <div class="row">

        <div class="col-md-3 column-adjustment-step-5 activity-page-left-panel-column-adjustment">
            <div class="activity-page-left-panel-div-block">
                <a href="../step-5" class="activity-page-back-link">&lt; Back</a>
                  <img src="/media/images/make-a-pledge2x.png" alt="" class="large-icon">
                  <div class="who-its-for-div-block">
                    <img src="/media/images/individual-icon.png" class="small-icon">
                    <div class="who-its-for">Individual</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="time-to-complete-div-block"><img src="/media/images/alarm-clock.png" class="small-icon">
                    <div class="time-to-complete">10 - 20 minutes</div>
                </div>
                <h1 class="activity-page-title">Prioritize and Make a Pledge</h1>
                <h2 class="activity-page-question">Why do this?</h2>
                <p class="activity-page-question-answer">To prioritize the ideas you have from your visioning and scorecard.</p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-md-9 right-panel-adjustment activity-page-right-panel-column-adjustment">

            <div class="div-block-7">
                <div class="div-block-6">
                    <h3 class="activity-heading-1 heading-color-adjustment">Make a Pledge</h3>

                    <p>What goals are you planning to achieve in the new year? Are they about preparing your house for climate change,
                       or protecting trees in your yard or block? Find out what your neighbours have been pledging, and work towards
                       the goals together!</p>
                    <br>


                        <div class="row margin-bottom-adjustment">
                            <div class="col-xs-12">
                                <h3 class="activity-heading-1 heading-color-adjustment">I PLEDGE</h3>
                                <p>e.g. plant a suitable tree that I like in my yard and take good care of it<br>
                                   e.g. water street trees on my clock during dry sessions<br>
                                   e.g. volunteer at least once at a City tree planting event with my family and/or neighbors</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xs-12">
                            <form novalidate onsubmit="return false" id="formTest">
                                <ul id="storyList" class="margin-left-adjustment">
                                    <label class="width-adjustment">
                                        <h4 class="storyheading">Pledge#1</h4>
                                        <textarea class="textarea-size-adjustment textarea-identifier"></textarea>
                                    </label>
                                </ul>

                                <div class="div-block-16">
                                    <input type="button" value="GENERATE PDF" id="generatePDF" class="btn btn-default button-1 leftbutton button-bottom-margin-adjustment" />
                                    <input type="button" value="ADD A PLEDGE" id="addPledge" class="btn btn-default button-1 leftbutton button-bottom-margin-adjustment" />
                                    <input type="button" value="REMOVE A PLEDGE" id="removePledge" class="btn btn-default button-1 button-bottom-margin-adjustment" />
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                        </div>



                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

